14
00:00:46.666 --> 00:00:48.100
A lot of people died

15
00:00:48.933 --> 00:00:50.900
Many families are separated

16
00:00:52.500 --> 00:00:53.566
Tianzai

17
00:00:54.766 --> 00:00:56.000
Undergraduate bar

18
00:00:57.000 --> 00:00:59.100
Were you there that day?

19
00:01:00.333 --> 00:01:02.300
My grandmother lives in Qingyun Town

20
00:01:02.300 --> 00:01:04.233
I lived there when I was a kid

21
00:01:04.533 --> 00:01:06.000
Then there was an earthquake.

22
00:01:06.000 --> 00:01:07.600
I went back to the North City

23
00:01:10.333 --> 00:01:11.766
Is it really weird?

24
00:01:11.900 --> 00:01:15.100
