28
00:01:22.266 --> 00:01:25.266
I was in the hospital that day.

29
00:01:25.533 --> 00:01:27.166
I accompany my mother to heal

30
00:01:27.733 --> 00:01:29.866
Really? Yeah?

31
00:01:30.300 --> 00:01:32.666
Dr. Xu is my mother's attending doctor

32
00:01:32.733 --> 00:01:35.900
